 padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 346.6pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 25.5pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"text-indent: 29.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\">有限责任公司分公司变更登记</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\\\\\"height: 34.45pt\\\\\">\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"119\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 89.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 34.45pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\">政策法规依据</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"462\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 346.6pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 34.45pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"text-indent: 29.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\">《中华人民共和国公司法》、《中华人民共和国公司登记管理条例》</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\\\\\"height: 34.35pt\\\\\">\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"119\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 89.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 34.35pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\">事项申办条件</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"462\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 346.6pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 34.35pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"text-indent: 24pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\">分公司变更登记事项的，应当向公司登记机关申请变更登记。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\\\\\"height: 210.3pt\\\\\">\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"119\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 89.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 210.3pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\">申报材料</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"462\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 346.6pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 210.3pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt\\\\\">１、公司法定代表人签署的《分公司变更登记申请书》；</div>\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt\\\\\">２、公司签署的《指定代表或者共同委托代理人的证明》及指定代表或委托代理人的身份证复印件；</div>\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt\\\\\">3、根据公司《章程》提交的决议；</div>\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt\\\\\">4、法律、行政法规规定分公司变更登记事项必须报经批准的，提交有关的批准文件或者许可证书复印件；</div>\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt\\\\\">5、因公司名称变更而申请变更分公司名称的，提交公司登记机关出具《准予变更登记通知书》复印件、变更后公司《企业法人营业执照》副本复印件；</div>\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt\\\\\">6、分公司变更经营范围提交公司《企业法人营业执照》副本复印件；分公司变更后经营范围涉及法律、行政法规和国务院决定规定必须在登记前报经批准的项目，提交有关的批准文件或者许可证书复印件或许可证明；</div>\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt\\\\\">7、分公司变更营业场所的，提交变更后营业场所的使用证明；</div>\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt\\\\\">8、分公司变更负责人的，提交公司出具的原任分公司负责人的免职文件和新任负责人的任职文件；填写《负责人登记表》。</div>\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt\\\\\">9、分公司的《营业执照》副本。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\\\\\"height: 25.5pt\\\\\">\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"119\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 89.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 25.5pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\">办理处理流程</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"462\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 346.6pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 25.5pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"text-indent: 29.75pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\">受理、审查、核准、发照</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\\\\\"height: 44.95pt\\\\\">\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"119\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 89.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; height: 44.95pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\">服务办理时限</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n 